sequenceDiagram
    Actor User
    Participant Runner
    Participant App
    Participant AllergyInfo
    Participant AllergyCSV
    User ->> Runner : Requests to update allergy
    Runner ->> App : Calls add_allergy_info(name, allergy)
    App ->> AllergyInfo : Calls update_allergy(name, new_allergy)
    AllergyInfo ->> AllergyCSV : Updates the CSV file with new allergy information